<p>Predictably, ad hominem abuse without analytical rebuttal.</p>
<p>For festive news without an ethnic dimension, try: </p>
<p>Hungry in Cameron&#8217;s Cotswolds: Beyond the 4x4s and classy shops of the PM&#8217;s own constituency, a food bank is alarmingly busy<br />
<a href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/hungry-in-camerons-cotswolds-beyond-the-4x4s-and-classy-shops-of-the-pms-own-constituency-a-food-bank-is-alarmingly-busy-9020229.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/hungry-in-camerons-cotswolds-beyond-the-4x4s-and-classy-shops-of-the-pms-own-constituency-a-food-bank-is-alarmingly-busy-9020229.html</a></p>
